name: Hand Knitted Army Green Cowl
description: This scarf is hand-knitted out of soft acrylic yarn. It is very lightweight but will also keep you warm. It can be worn as an addition to your fall outfit, under or over your fall or winter coat. It measures 15 inches when lying flat and is 11 inches wide. This army green scarf stretches over your head and is one size fits all. With this bright accessory you are sure to standout in a crowd.

name: hand Knitted Dark Red Turban
description: This turban is hand knitted out of baby alpaca yarn.  This is a very soft and warm yarn and will keep you fashionable and warm at that same time. This Turban is one size fits all and I have it in many other colors. If you would prefer it in another color  please email me at fuzzyflirt@gmail.com

name: Hand Knitted Yellow And Tan Hat
description: This hat is the perfect accessory to your fall and winter wardrobe. It measures 21 inches high when laid flat and is one size fits all. It is hand knitted out of acrylic yellow and tan yarn. This hat has a stretchy nature to it so it will fit a male or a female. It can be worn as a slouchy hat or can be folded at the bottom and worn as a skull cap. This hat is will not only have you looking stylish but will keep your head warm too.
